name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: insite - never lose a thought again

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GET A GRIP ON YOUR DIGITAL WORKSPACE

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
insite is the simplest way to keep track of all your ideas, resources and documents

Quick and convenient, insite’s pop-out sidebar lets you create notes and tasks as you browse.

Designed for you, and for working with others - use insite on your own, then connect and privately share notes, ideas and tasks.

FEATURES & BENEFITS
- Instant access as you browse - quicker than switching tabs and pasting URLs
- All-in-one: notes, tasks and messages - simpler than using multiple apps
- One feed for all your stuff - an easy way to manage all your workstreams

You can also upgrade to a team licence at any time.

• • •

For more information visit https://www.insite.life/
